<body>
<div type="letter">
<pb facs="1038129" n="1"/>
  
<opener>
  <note hand="pers_DE-588-119166895">Ad <abbr>Dnum</abbr> <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-119112450">Hermannum</rs>.</note>
  <dateline><date when="1715-12-23">23. Xbris 1715</date>.</dateline>
<lb/><salute>Viro Celeberrimo et Doctissimo
  <rs type="person">Jacobo Herma<choice><orig><g ref="#nn">n̄</g></orig><reg>nn</reg></choice>o</rs>
  <abbr>S. P. D.</abbr>
  <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-119166895">N. B.</rs></salute>
</opener>
  <p><lb/>Accepi haud ita pridem <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> <abbr>Rev.</abbr> <abbr>D.</abbr> <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-1048628825">Parente</rs> Tuo <add>exemplum</add> doctissimi operis
  <lb/>Tui de <rs type="biblio">Viribus et Motibus corporum</rs> exempl<supplied>.</supplied> pro quo eximio
  <lb/>dono Tibi debitas ago gratias. Gratulor vehementer, et Tibi, quod rem<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>publicam literariam tam egregie locupleta<add>veris</add>, et mihi, quod tam lucu<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>lentum perennantis erga me amiciti<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> tu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> testimonium mihi
  <lb/>ex hibere volueris, transmissione elegantis istius operis, cujus
  <lb/>lectione su<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>a cum voluptate defuncturus spero, me non exigua
  <lb/>studiis meis Mathematicis incrementa adjecturum. Statim quidem
  <lb/>ac donum istud Tuum accepi,<!-- To Do: Komma kontrollieren--> maximo desiderio ardens videndi locum
  <lb/>in <rs type="letter">epistola</rs> Tua die <date when="1715-10-11">11. <abbr>Oct.</abbr></date> ad <rs type="person">Patruum</rs> missa <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> Te citatum, ubi <rs type="keyword">Pro<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>blema <add>inversum</add> virium centralium</rs> pro omnibus curvis algebraicis
  <lb/>generali aliqua formula <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> Te solutum esse dixisti, locum eum
  <lb/>evolvi, sed ut verum fate<add>a</add>r, inveni ibi tantum solutionem Pro<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>blematis directi, quo ex data <rs type="keyword">curva algebraica</rs> qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>ritur scala
  <lb/>virium, et quod in potestate esse nemo unquam negavit. Sed <add>pro</add> data qua<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>libet scala virium invenire curvam trajectoriam algebraicam
  <lb/>isti legi satisfacientem, Problema est altioris indaginis imo tale
  <lb/>quod possibilitatis limites transilire etiamnum asseverare
  <lb/>audeo. Ad ejus <add>enim</add> solutionem requiritur ut in <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>quatione tua generali
    <lb/>§<choice><orig><g ref="#ndot">.</g></orig><reg></reg></choice> 169<choice><orig><g ref="#ndot">.</g></orig><reg></reg></choice> tradita <formula>G=\frac{1}{z^{3}}+\frac{(2ssB+ssCz\mp eB^{2}z\pm4eAB\pm2eACz+AB^{5}z-2A^{2}B-A^{2}Cz)\cdot nn}{B^{3}z{5}</formula>,
    <lb/>ex data quantitate <formula>G</formula>, inveniantur quantitates
  <lb/><formula>A</formula>, <formula>B</formula>, <formula>C</formula>, non autem, ut ex datis quantitat<add>ibus <foreign>ABC</foreign>, inveniatur quan</add><pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>titas <formula>G</formula>, <add>id</add> quod tu fecisti et quod ut jam dixi nil aliud est quam solutio
  <lb/>Problematis directi. Prius autem illud impossibile esse, non dubito
  <lb/>quin mecum agniturus sis. Si tamen, quod non spero, egomet
  <pb facs="1038130" n="2"/>
    <lb/>fallor, peto ut mihi saltem monstres quomodo ex dicta <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>quatione
    <lb/>§<choice><orig><g ref="#ndot">.</g></orig><reg></reg></choice> 169<choice><orig><g ref="#ndot">.</g></orig><reg></reg></choice> erui possit <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>quatio <add>curv<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> algebraic<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></add> qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> satisfaciat huic legi <rs type="keyword">virium centra<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>lium</rs> <choice><orig><formula>G=\frac{z^{3}+\overline{aa-zz}\sqrt{aa+zz}}{zz}</formula></orig><reg><formula>G=\frac{z^{3}+(aa-zz)\sqrt{aa+zz}}{zz}</formula></reg></choice>. C<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>terum gaudeo Tibi displicere
    <lb/>litem <add>illam inutilem</add> quam <rs type="person">Riccatus</rs> Tui defendendi causa <add>sine necessitate</add> excitavit; testimonium
    <lb/>istud <add>T</add>uum inserui alteri me<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> responsioni, quam <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-119543885">Riccati</rs> cavilla<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tionibus reponere necesse habui, quod ut puto non male feres.
    <lb/>Lis enim h<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>c minus te respicit <choice><orig><g ref="#klammerauf">|:</g></orig><reg>(</reg></choice>utpote qui nulla defensione egebas,
    <lb/>qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> enim monuerat <rs type="person" key="">Patruus</rs> bonitati <add>et eleganti<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></add> <rs type="biblio">solutionis</rs> Tu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> nihil
    <lb/>derogant<choice><orig><g ref="#klammerzu">:|</g></orig><reg>)</reg></choice> quam ipsum <abbr>D.</abbr> <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-119543885">Riccatum</rs>, quem nimis arroganter de se
    <lb/><unclear>a</unclear>t nimis contemtim de <rs type="persons">Bernoulliis</rs> sensisse (<add>ut apparet</add> ex multis ejus expressio<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>nibus, quales sunt <abbr>ex. gr.</abbr> <cit><quote><foreign xml:lang="ita"><hi rend="u">sandagliato da essi tutto il fondo della lor
  <lb/>Geometria <add><choice><orig><g ref="#etlig">&amp;</g></orig><reg>et</reg></choice>c.</add></hi></foreign></quote></cit>, <cit><quote><foreign xml:lang="ita"><hi rend="u">mi si conceda che nel caso nostro non trovano luogo
  <lb/>le loro sublimi fatich<choice><orig><g ref="#egrav">è</g></orig><reg>e</reg></choice></hi></foreign></quote></cit>,<note type="editorial">Es ist nicht eindeutig zu entscheiden, ob das Zitat unterbrochen ist oder ob zwei separate Zitate intendiert sind.</note> ali<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>que plure<unclear>s</unclear>) Tu ipse indigne feres.
    <lb/>Problema <rs type="persons">Geometris Italis</rs> propositum <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> multis solutum fuisse
    <lb/>significarunt <rs type="persons">Editores</rs> <rs type="biblio">Diarii Veneti</rs>, sed credat <rs type="person">Jud<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>us Apella</rs>;<note type="comment">Zitat von Horaz nachweisen.</note>
    <lb/>ego omnino credo <add><choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice></add> <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-117596027">Zendrin<add>o</add></rs> cui parabolam cubicam <add>te nomin</add>asse
    <lb/>scimus, ad reliquos notitiam hujus curv<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> pervenisse. Optassem ne
    <lb/><add><rs type="person">Zendrino</rs></add> quicquam patefecisses, sic enim ipsi et aliis <rs type="persons">Italis</rs> superbis
    <lb/>occasio defuisset<note type="editorial">Die Streichung der vorangehenden zwei Wörter wurde durch Hinzufügen von Punkten wieder rückgängig gemacht.</note> <add>uno conclamandi ore me</add> <rs type="biblio">Problematis</rs> tam facilis propositione <add>nil nisi</add> contemt<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice>
    <lb/>erga <rs type="persons">Italos</rs> prodidisse, id quod imprimis
    <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-117596027">Zendrinum</rs> questum fuisse <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> <abbr>D.</abbr> <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-118571249">Leibnitio</rs> scimus. Tandem
    <lb/>est quod <add>T</add>e rogem de duobus qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> pridem scire desidero. Primum
    <lb/>num <rs type="letter">epistolam</rs> meam in Tuo per <rs type="place" key="place_GEO-2950159">Berolinum</rs> transitu <abbr>D.</abbr> <rs type="person">Cunoni</rs>
    <lb/>tradideris, et quomodo illa excepta fuerit. Alterum, an nihil
    <lb/>Tibi constet de <rs type="biblio">schedis</rs> in quibus defunctus <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-118509969">Patruus</rs> meus
    <lb/>enumerationem <rs type="keyword">linearum tertii ordinis</rs> descripsit, mallem
    <lb/>scire in quant<add>um</add> conveniat cum <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-118587544">Newtoni</rs> enumeratione <add>earundem</add>
    <lb/>curvarum.</p> <closer><salute>Interim Vale novumque quem propediem auspi<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>cabimur a<choice><orig><g ref="#nn">n̄</g></orig><reg>nn</reg></choice>um, pluresque sequentes feliciter transige.</salute></closer>
</div>
